FBIS3-14317 "drnes058_n_94008" FBIS-NES-94-058 Document Type:Daily Report 23 Mar 1994 LEBANON Al-Hariri Receives U.S. Message on South NC2303132594 Beirut Voice of Lebanon in Arabic 1215 GMT 23 Mar 94 NC2303132594 Beirut Voice of Lebanon Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Excerpt] U.S. Ambassador to Lebanon Mark Hambley, who visited Prime Minister Rafiq al-Hariri today, said he conveyed a message from the U.S. Government to the Lebanese Government on the tragic situation in the south. [passage omitted]
